data.title: Robert Simpson Woodward on Mount Wilson
data.meta_description: Robert Simpson Woodward (president of the Carnegie Institute of Washington ) on Mount Wilson. Mr. Woodward is wearing a suit and a hat. He's standing on a rock, with trees behind him. Tree-covered mountainsides are in the background.Image courtesy of the Observatories of the Carnegie Institution for Science Collection at the Huntington Library, San Marino, California.
